@GetMapping("/hello/{name}")
@ResponseBody
public ResponseEntity<String> hello(@PathVariable String name) {
    CacheControl cacheControl = CacheControl.maxAge(60, TimeUnit.SECONDS)
      .noTransform()
      .mustRevalidate();
    return ResponseEntity.ok()
      .cacheControl(cacheControl)
      .body("Hello " + name);
}
```

